    "body": "@taktoa I didn't know that, thanks for sharing.\r\n\r\nThe problem is `.desktop` is a complete different thing from shortcut links on Windows, `.desktop` has to be put in certain paths and it is desktop environment's responsibility to decide where to show the app's icon, while shortcuts links are just files that can be put anywhere like symbol links.\r\n\r\n\r\n"
